text:
Result data file is written by xml format, and its description of encoding 
is 'UTF-8'.
But actual result data file's encoding is not any encoding.

The following modify enable a correct result data file for multibyte chaset
(i.e. japanese, chinese, korean, ...).

diff -rcbB -I '^// 
$Header:' ./core/org/apache/jmeter/reporters/ResultCollector.java /home/shuyo/jm
eter/jakarta-jmeter-
2.0.0/src/core/org/apache/jmeter/reporters/ResultCollector.java
*** ./core/org/apache/jmeter/reporters/ResultCollector.java	Mon Mar  8 
08:33:03 2004
--- /home/shuyo/jmeter/jakarta-jmeter-
2.0.0/src/core/org/apache/jmeter/reporters/ResultCollector.java	Thu Apr  8 
16:07:05 2004
***************
